Name: Name Change, Robert Rodriguez Place, Manhattan
Title: A Local Law in relation to a street name, Robert Rodriguez Place, Borough of Manhattan.
Text:
Be it enacted by the Council as follows:
	Section 1.  The following street name is hereby designated as hereafter indicated.

New Name				Present Name			Limits

Robert Rodriguez Place                    East 120th Street                    between First Avenue
                                                                                                        and Pleasant Avenue
      
      
      ï¿½  2.  This local law shall take effect immediately.
